	Why we added it

	In a multi-tenant system, this is safer:

	/api/tenants/{tenantId}/users/{userId}

	than this:

	/api/users/{userId}

	because every user lookup is constrained by tenantId.

	What you need to remember

	This repository method is important:

	findByTenantIdAndId(UUID tenantId, UUID userId)

	It ensures the user belongs to the requested tenant. This is one of the earliest foundations of tenant isolation.

