Deactivate Tenant:
	What we added
    DELETE /api/tenants/{id}
    Tenant soft delete behavior
    Tenant deactivation logic
    Why we added it

    In SaaS systems, tenants should usually not be physically deleted because they may have users, subscriptions, billing records, audit logs, and historical data.

    So we keep the tenant record and mark it inactive.

    What you need to remember

    This is called soft delete.

    The API uses:

    DELETE /api/tenants/{id}

    But internally we do:

    tenant.setStatus(TenantStatus.INACTIVE);

    So the record remains in the database.


